      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 4,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 5,
      "text": "TO : Director, FBI",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 6,
      "text": "DATE: September 27, 1947",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 7,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 8,
      "text": "FROM : SAC, Butte",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 10,
      "text": "SUBJECT: FLYING DISCS SIGHTED MAY 5, 1947,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 11,
      "text": "BETWEEN ELLENSBURG AND SEATTLE, WASHINGTON",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 13,
      "text": "[REDACTED] Montana State Prison, Deer Lodge, Montana, has",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 14,
      "text": "advised the writer that while driving between Ellensburg and Seattle, Washing-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 15,
      "text": "ton, about 3:30 P.M., on May 5, 1947, he sighted a silver object streaking",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 16,
      "text": "across the sky. This was also seen by [REDACTED], convict chauffeur,",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 17,
      "text": "and [REDACTED] This object went into a nose dive and they thought it would",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 18,
      "text": "crash. However, before reaching the earth it disintegrated, leaving a long",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 19,
      "text": "pillar of \"gas\" hanging in the sky. It was particularly odd because this re-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 20,
      "text": "mained in form and did not blow away. It was observed by these three people",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21,
      "text": "while they drove from twenty to thirty miles.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 22,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 23,
      "text": "This smoky, gaseous pillar was a long ways off and remained high",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 24,
      "text": "in the air. [REDACTED] said that this silver object was traveling at an",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 25,
      "text": "excessively high rate of speed and when it disintegrated it was still a long",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 26,
      "text": "way from the earth. [REDACTED] said when he first saw it he thought it was",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 27,
      "text": "probably a jet propelled plane but that he couldn't tell except that its mo-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 28,
      "text": "tions were erratic. He said he had not reported it until he had noticed so",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 29,
      "text": "much in the papers about these discs. Although three people saw it, they de-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 30,
      "text": "cided that they must be \"seeing things\".",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32,
      "text": "The Seattle Office is requested to advise Mr. [REDACTED] 4th",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 33,
      "text": "Air Force, S-2, McChord Field, Washington.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 34,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 35,
      "text": "No further action is being taken by the Butte Office due to the",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 36,
      "text": "time elapsing between the sighting of this object and the report.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
